other_tests.findings: Phe level in the classic range at 1642 μmol/L and a second level of 1492 μmol/L obtained a few days later.
The patient was found to be homozygous for a three-basepair in-frame deletion variant c.169_171del, p.Glu57del in the PAH gene, consistent with the genetic diagnosis of autosomal recessive PKU.
